{"tid":2428096,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有8083有贊科技","createTime":"2021-03-01T10:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T04:54:22.000Z","uid":51578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c517750fdcc88e4712fc5066c4229c16791bb5e1","tid":2428096,"uid":51578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:03:55.000Z","msg":"睇完個通告都好迷<br />\n好似唔同人解讀完全唔同<br />\n有無巴打分析下<br />\n<br />\n3.8有幾手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba0710e8f6ad34b19fd1b2fe05edc7b4b43bda8","tid":2428096,"uid":51578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"中國有贊至岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177596f40dd22a9e090b0c83bec0732526b21698","tid":2428096,"uid":322822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"知道ceo 被人拉左"},{"pid":"83d8544c5f40f72cc81bf01bd584ce28313776a1","tid":2428096,"uid":216709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:12:46.000Z","msg":"copy 番黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n中國有贊(<a href=\"http://8083.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F8083.HK&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt13f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=e8d1de9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">8083.HK</a>)︰(i)向全體中國有贊股東（包括中國有贊除外股東）分派中國有贊所持有的有贊科技股份 ; (ii)於完成分派後，根據公司法第99條以計劃安排方式將中國有贊私有化。<br />\n阿斯點評︰其實今日睇呢單應該夠。首先，我建議大家避一避比較好。當然，如果你想知點解，我簡單講下有關操作︰<br />\n1. 文件中表示，因為支付業務前景一般，所以私有化中國有贊(8083)，所以將其SAAS業務分將有贊科技(科技)於主板上市<br />\n2. 條款就係以1股(8083) 換0.05077265股(科技) + $0.1352<br />\n= （由於仲量聯11月時估值(科技)大概係$42/股），所以每作價係2.3088，對比起現價（$3.32）大概折讓3成。<br />\n五個重點︰<br />\n1. 背後原因極有機會係因為有贊條數太難轉主板上市條件，所以寧願用這個方式轉主板。<br />\n2. 仲量聯個估值係11月時做，但畢竟有大幅折讓，要約人表示不會提價，就看看之後會否再提高估值。<br />\n3. 如果用星期五收市價$3.32比較，(科技)上市時價格就要$62/股才會打和。<br />\n4. 由於現價已經比最終作價有所提高3成，所以小股東是否持有就要視乎大家對於新業務再上市後會否有大幅上升。<br />\n5. 如果都係不明白程序就用當日海爾電器私有化，及智家(<a href=\"http://6690.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F6690.HK&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt13f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=2ee4abd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">6690.HK</a>)上市的情況比較就可以。"},{"pid":"a430630056bb86bcc9298659de3e6d6a8d26eb32","tid":2428096,"uid":109155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T17:33:26.000Z","msg":"4蚊有10手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講短線應該好難上返去"},{"pid":"66a78fb011c83679285a0c5af5ceb94ac0e189f6","tid":2428096,"uid":184726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"你當而家8083係暗盤就得<br />\n2.3係招股價"},{"pid":"af9e583b4ac4cb4c99ed18058cb69981aacc1c65","tid":2428096,"uid":119814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T00:18:57.000Z","msg":"呢個寫得不錯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%9c%89%e8%b4%8a-8083-%e7%a7%81%e6%9c%89%e5%8c%96-%e4%b8%8a%e5%b8%82-%e8%b2%a1%e6%8a%80%e6%93%8d%e4%bd%9c%e4%b9%8b%e8%ac%8e-249180/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2F%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25b3%2587%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%259c%2589%25e8%25b4%258a-8083-%25e7%25a7%2581%25e6%259c%2589%25e5%258c%2596-%25e4%25b8%258a%25e5%25b8%2582-%25e8%25b2%25a1%25e6%258a%2580%25e6%2593%258d%25e4%25bd%259c%25e4%25b9%258b%25e8%25ac%258e-249180%2F&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt13f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=d9b00148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%9c%89%e8%b4%8a-8083-%e7%a7%81%e6%9c%89%e5%8c%96-%e4%b8%8a%e5%b8%82-%e8%b2%a1%e6%8a%80%e6%93%8d%e4%bd%9c%e4%b9%8b%e8%ac%8e-249180/</a>"},{"pid":"33148e75e463cac8576320a6c0016c94eaae3c8a","tid":2428096,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T00:31:05.000Z","msg":"睇唔明既人，呢幾日都會放。大上大落"},{"pid":"dc5aea9d64155fadf31b6a11d99800e1d9deb91a","tid":2428096,"uid":132466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a430630056bb8